  "detailed_description": "Halley's Dream is a beautiful third-person adventure game about a husky dog that woke up in a beautiful fantasy world. He will find that all other animals except one bear are turned into a stone by an evil dragon. Along the way, the player will experience a relaxed, dreamlike atmosphere, solve mysteries, and explore a beautiful world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Beautiful storyline</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/1b50ef759d36123f864a2904938e072b.poster.avif?t=1717930586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/1b50ef759d36123f864a2904938e072b.webm?t=1717930586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/1b50ef759d36123f864a2904938e072b.mp4?t=1717930586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Various movement mechanics</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/86c6b2501073b4a86d6ec07b3836c34f.poster.avif?t=1717930586\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/86c6b2501073b4a86d6ec07b3836c34f.webm?t=1717930586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425830/extras/86c6b2501073b4a86d6ec07b3836c34f.mp4?t=1717930586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2>You will travel through the world by following the beautiful storyline, solve interesting puzzles, learn new abilities by collecting items.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beautiful fantasy world with interesting puzzles to solve.<br></li><li>Cozy and dreamlike experience.<br></li><li>Compelling and memorable storyline.<br></li><li>This is a short 1.5 - 2.5h to complete game.<br></li><li>Play on your own pace - there is no need to finish the game fast, you are free to explore the world.</li></ul></h2></h2></h2></h2>",
